summary: Can fight with a fishing rod.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/36467-1-1369664746.png[/img]
Hey Guys,
This is part of a number of mods i am going to make, where little things around skyrim which have no use will be given, a use.

this is just a little mod i made, where you can pick up fishing rods(outside the Riften house, \"Honeyside\".), and yes, use them as weapons(like assassins creed).
well they have pretty low stats,(come on, its just a piece of wood with a hook!)
they are craftable at a forge,(under wood).
*and yes, i know the title is ridiculous*
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Look out for Master Of weapons - Lumberjack\'s Hook, it will be out soon.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
author: Daren
